'''Brandyfoot''' was a family of [[Harfoots]] that travelled in a [[Wandering Days|wandering]] caravan that was led by [[Sadoc Burrows]] sometime during the [[Second Age]].

The family and its members were invented by [[Amazon Studios]] for ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]''.<ref>{{webcite|author=The Lord of the Rings on Prime|articleurl=https://twitter.com/LOTRonPrime/status/1493253881651937283|articlename=Markella Kavenagh is Elanor ‘Nori’ Brandyfoot|dated=14 February 2022|website=[https://twitter.com Twitter]|accessed=27 July 2023}}</ref><ref>{{webcite|author=The Lord of the Rings on Prime|articleurl=https://twitter.com/LOTRonPrime/status/1534982400869945344#m|articlename=Dylan Smith is Largo Brandyfoot. #LOTRROP|dated=9 June 2022|website=[https://twitter.com Twitter]|accessed=27 July 2023}}</ref><ref>{{webcite|author=The Lord of the Rings on Prime|articleurl=https://twitter.com/LOTRonPrime/status/1534982566448533504#m|articlename=Sara Zwangobani is Marigold Brandyfoot. #LOTRROP|dated=9 June 2022|website=[https://twitter.com Twitter]|accessed=27 July 2023}}</ref>

